---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About ShippingCalc" description="ShippingCalc provides free shipping rate calculators for Shopify sellers.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto prose prose-sky">
    <h1>About ShippingCalc</h1>
    <p>ShippingCalc is a free resource for Shopify sellers who want to understand and reduce their shipping costs. We built these tools because carrier pricing is opaque, and most rate calculators are buried inside apps that require a monthly subscription.</p>
    <p>Our calculators are free, require no login, and are updated regularly as carrier rates change.</p>
    <p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> ShippingCalc is an independent resource. We are not affiliated with or endorsed by Shopify Inc., USPS, UPS, or FedEx.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
